arStrings.szText: Lilith has been defeated, but there is still much to do. Level up to take on new challenges across the continent.

Complete {c_highlight}Whispers of the Dead{/c}, participate in {c_highlight}Helltide{/c}, and challenge yourself in {c_highlight}Nightmare Dungeons{/c} to gain valuable items and crafting materials to progress your character.
Continue unlocking World Tiers to gain access to more features and powerful items.
When you are strong enough, face the Echo of Lilith in the final World Tier.
